sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Mirror runtime
    participant C as Control plane
    participant X as Master model<br/>(Claude Sonnet 4.6)
    participant V as Vision-capable device
    participant L as Luxo runtime
    participant LA as Luxo agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)
    participant H as Chef runtime
    participant HA as Chef agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)
    participant MA as Mirror agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)

    Note over U,HA: DETERMINISTIC COMMAND (no model on either side)
    U->>M: "Luxo blue"
    M->>M: VAD + Whisper
    M->>C: DeviceEvent(kind=transcript)
    C->>C: deterministic route: match
    C-->>L: command: set_color blue
    L->>L: direct command handler (no model)
    L->>L: execute hardware
    L-->>C: action_result

    Note over U,HA: REASONING PATH (two-tier model)
    U->>M: "I need to lock in"
    M->>M: VAD + Whisper
    M->>C: DeviceEvent(kind=transcript)
    C->>C: router: no deterministic match
    C->>X: assembled prompt + tools
    X-->>C: tool_use: update_user_state + spawn_luxo + spawn_chef + spawn_mirror
    C->>C: persist state.json

    par Master dispatches NL intents to devices
        C-->>L: spawn: "Set a deep focus scene - dim blue light, slow calm breathing pattern"
        C-->>H: spawn: "Bring a glass of water, say 'staying hydrated for the grind'"
        C-->>M: spawn: "Say something encouraging about locking in"
    end

    Note over L,LA: Device agent loops (parallel)
    L->>LA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    LA->>LA: plan: set_color(blue, brightness=40), animate(breathe, slow)
    LA-->>L: tool calls
    L->>L: execute hardware
    LA->>LA: check: done
    L-->>C: action_result

    H->>HA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    HA->>HA: plan: drive_to(desk), extend_tray, speak(msg)
    HA-->>H: tool calls
    H->>H: execute hardware
    HA->>HA: check: done
    H-->>C: action_result

    M->>MA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    MA->>MA: plan: speak(encouragement)
    MA-->>M: tool calls
    M->>M: execute hardware
    MA->>MA: check: done
    M-->>C: action_result

    Note over U,HA: VISION PATH
    V->>V: motion gate + frame capture
    V->>C: DeviceEvent(kind=frame, image_b64)
    C->>C: vision.py: Claude Vision analysis
    C->>C: significant mood change detected
    C->>C: enqueue vision_result event
    C->>X: vision_result + state + recent context
    X-->>C: tool_use: update_user_state + spawn_luxo + spawn_mirror
    C->>C: persist state.json

    par Master dispatches NL intents
        C-->>L: spawn: "Shift to warm relaxing light, gentle sway"
        C-->>M: spawn: "Suggest taking a break, sound caring"
    end

    L->>LA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    LA-->>L: tool calls
    L->>L: execute hardware
    L-->>C: action_result

    M->>MA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    MA-->>M: tool calls
    M->>M: execute hardware
    M-->>C: action_result
